# Claude Code Prompt — DCC v0.3 Refactor: Validate and Implement

## Context

You are working on the `drive_cycle_calculator` Python package (`dcc`). This task has
three phases. **Stop and report at the end of each phase — do not proceed to the next
phase until the user explicitly confirms.**

**Before doing anything else, read both of the following in full:**

1. `docs/designs/refactor_v0.3.md` — the authoritative design document for this refactor.
   All section references in this prompt (e.g. "Section 3.1") refer to headings in
   that document.
2. `brainstorming/refactor-proposals/clarification-v0.3.md` — the pre-refactor codebase
   audit report. This documents the old architecture and known inconsistencies, and is
   the factual baseline for Phase 1 validation.

All generated reports from this sprint are to be written under
`brainstorming/refactor-proposals/` with a `-v0.3` suffix, for traceability.

